	<clause id="_subscription_to_shared_calendars" obligation="normative"><title>Subscription to shared calendars</title><p id="_2aa9b486-a84a-49f1-b948-caac3006694c">Malicious events can end up in user calendars through shared calendars.</p>
	<p id="_f00f1331-efd0-4a6e-b162-36ba59bd5540">Shared calendars are have a single origin and users are subscribed to its events,
